        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="bg-white rounded-2xl border border-gray-100 p-7 flex gap-5 shadow-sm">
        <div class="w-11 h-11 rounded-xl bg-accent/25 flex items-center justify-center shrink-0 text-xl">↩️</div>
        <div>
          <h3 class="font-bold text-gray-900 mb-1">One-click refunds</h3>
          <p class="text-sm text-gray-500 leading-relaxed">Release a client's hold instantly from your dashboard the moment they walk through the door.</p>
        </div>
